sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as Open WebUI
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant G as Qwen3Guard
    participant ASR as Qwen3-ASR
    participant VLM as Qwen3-VL
    participant RET as Retriever/Qdrant
    participant R as Reranker
    participant LLM as Qwen3.5-4B

    U->>UI: Send text/audio/image
    UI->>API: Request

    alt Audio
        API->>ASR: Transcribe audio
        ASR-->>API: Transcript
    end

    alt Image/Chart
        API->>VLM: Analyze image/chart
        VLM-->>API: Structured text summary
    end

    API->>G: Check input safety
    G-->>API: safe / unsafe

    alt Input unsafe
        API-->>UI: Default apology
    else Input safe
        API->>RET: Hybrid retrieve
        RET-->>API: Top-k chunks
        API->>R: Rerank
        R-->>API: Ranked context
        API->>LLM: Generate answer
        LLM-->>API: Draft answer
        API->>G: Check output safety
        G-->>API: safe / unsafe

        alt Output unsafe
            API->>LLM: Retry with safety feedback
            LLM-->>API: New answer
            API->>G: Re-check output
            G-->>API: safe / unsafe
        end

        alt Final safe
            API-->>UI: Answer + citations
        else Final unsafe
            API-->>UI: Default apology
        end
    end